K8fArF",2025-01-24T03:00:00.000Z,,,True,,,"Default Settings
- damage level 2
- timer 99","Brook Wingman Converters will be provided rather than requiring players bring their own. Converters are put in force digital mode (LED on the new model converter should be blue). This is more strictly enforced if a persons controller is capable of an uncleaned socd whether pure dpad or dpad + analog stick.
Instant super buttons are banned. Converter remap function is allowed, turbo not. (Please reset the converter bindings to default when you hop off if you use this function)

Pause penalty: round loss. Enforced as player eating penalty has to afk for the rest of the round

